sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Dev as Blueprint Push (Main)
    participant Atomic as Atomic Action Workflows
    participant Security as OSS Security Scanners
    participant Reg as GitHub Registry (ghcr.io)
    participant Assembler as Assembler Action Workflows
    
    Dev->>Atomic: Trigger `.github/workflows/build-glibc.yml`
    activate Atomic
    
    Atomic->>Security: Execute SAST (Semgrep) on C-source
    Security-->>Atomic: Pass
    Atomic->>Atomic: Compile native `.so` files
    Atomic->>Security: Execute SCA/SBOM generation (Trivy/Syft)
    Security-->>Atomic: Pass (Outputs glibc-sbom.json)
    Atomic->>Security: Sign artifact manifest (Cosign)
    
    Atomic->>Reg: Push intermediate artifact `opensource-distroless/artifacts-glibc`
    deactivate Atomic
    
    note over Reg, Assembler: Once glibc, openssl, zlib, tzdata are updated in Registry...
    
    Assembler->>Reg: `.github/workflows/assemble-base.yml` runs
    activate Assembler
    Assembler->>Reg: Pull isolated atomic artifacts
    Reg-->>Assembler: Download Verified `.tar.gz` and SBOMs
    
    Assembler->>Assembler: Construct `FROM Scratch` monolithic base
    Assembler->>Security: Sign aggregated final OCI manifest
    Assembler->>Reg: Push `opensource-distroless/base:latest`
    deactivate Assembler
    
    Reg-->>Assembler: Triggers `assemble-cc.yml` upon base success
